message.content:
The age of an 18-year-old 50 years ago would be 68 years old now. 

Here's the math: 
- They were 18 in (current year - 50), or a birth year of (2022 - 50) = 1972
- Their current age is calculated as (current year - birthyear) 
=Our subject would be (2022 – 1972)
=They would be, therefore, at present time, aged around ’68’.
